00:02:27.113 --> 00:02:29.215 line:95%,end
You are getting a solo this weekend.

00:02:30.450 --> 00:02:32.285 line:95%,end
All right, Chloe, Maddie,

00:02:32.352 --> 00:02:34.621 line:95%,end
you are also getting solos this weekend.

00:02:35.255 --> 00:02:36.122 line:95%,end
