00:03:06.686 --> 00:03:08.054 line:95%,end
Yes? Sit up straight.

00:03:08.121 --> 00:03:09.622 line:95%,end
Ladies, let's go.

00:03:09.689 --> 00:03:11.324 line:95%,end
<i>Competing locally in Pittsburgh</i>

00:03:11.391 --> 00:03:12.458 line:95%,end
