00:03:12.525 --> 00:03:15.562 line:95%,end
<i>It's a big deal because my name</i>
<i>and my reputation are on the line.</i>

00:03:15.628 --> 00:03:17.397 line:5%,start
<i>So we have a lot of work to do.</i>

00:03:19.465 --> 00:03:22.202 line:5%,start
It's like you're dancing
out of control a little bit.

00:03:22.268 --> 00:03:23.736 line:5%,start
You need to bring it down.

00:03:23.803 --> 00:03:24.704 line:5%,start
Yes.

00:03:24.771 --> 00:03:26.372 line:5%,start
