00:03:36.683 --> 00:03:38.084 line:95%,end
<i>I love solo work.</i>

00:03:38.151 --> 00:03:41.387 line:95%,end
<i>I love the one on one work</i>
<i>with the student.</i>

00:03:41.454 --> 00:03:44.657 line:95%,end
<i>I think every child grows</i>
<i>from doing a solo.</i>

