of that dance jail.

00:05:43.309 --> 00:05:45.044 line:95%,end
<i>This time, we invited Cathy to come along</i>

00:05:45.111 --> 00:05:46.212 line:95%,end
<i>because she's new to the group</i>

00:05:46.279 --> 00:05:47.513 line:95%,end
and we wanted to feel like, you know,

00:05:47.580 --> 00:05:49.048 line:95%,end
