00:05:49.115 --> 00:05:51.117 line:95%,end
So what did you guys think
of the competition this weekend?

00:05:51.184 --> 00:05:52.452 line:95%,end
It was far away,

00:05:52.518 --> 00:05:53.453 line:95%,end
too far away.

00:05:53.519 --> 00:05:55.521 line:95%,end
I mean, we sat there.
