00:05:55.588 --> 00:05:56.723 line:95%,end
You're right, I did.

00:05:56.789 --> 00:05:57.890 line:95%,end
All right, guys,

00:05:57.957 --> 00:05:59.726 line:95%,end
-we will see you later.
-Are you leaving?

00:05:59.792 --> 00:06:01.394 line:95%,end
