00:06:16.242 --> 00:06:18.211 line:95%,end
at the competitions. I'm sorry.

00:06:18.277 --> 00:06:19.212 line:95%,end
That's upsetting for us

00:06:19.278 --> 00:06:20.880 line:95%,end
because I think we all care

00:06:20.947 --> 00:06:23.049 line:95%,end
-about the kids and those dancers.
-Yeah.

00:06:23.116 --> 00:06:26.519 line:95%,end
Yeah. I--and if you don't want us
to be cheerleaders, that's fine,

00:06:26.586 --> 00:06:28.688 line:95%,end
but I like supporting the other kids.

00:06:28.755 --> 00:06:31.924 line:95%,end
