00:06:41.334 --> 00:06:43.035 line:95%,end
<i>You know, I'm looking at the clock</i>

00:06:43.102 --> 00:06:44.203 line:95%,end
<i>when I'm sitting there</i>

00:06:44.270 --> 00:06:46.205 line:95%,end
<i>and I'm thinking of all of the things</i>

00:06:46.272 --> 00:06:47.273 line:95%,end
