00:07:27.280 --> 00:07:28.748 line:95%,end
<i>Oh, yes, I'm brutally honest.</i>

00:07:28.815 --> 00:07:30.116 line:95%,end
I have to be.

00:07:30.183 --> 00:07:31.517 line:95%,end
That leg, yes?

00:07:31.584 --> 00:07:32.585 line:95%,end
Do it again.

00:07:32.652 --> 00:07:34.720 line:95%,end
<i>That final product onstage</i>

00:07:34.787 --> 00:07:37.390 line:95%,end
<i>is what all the hours of training</i>
<i>are about.</i>

00:07:37.457 --> 00:07:38.958 line:95%,end
This is my job.

00:07:39.025 --> 00:07:40.226 line:95%,end
This is what I do.

00:07:41.527 --> 00:07:42.762 line:95%,end
I don't know why
you're leaning in the heels,

00:07:42.829 --> 00:07:43.663 line:95%,end
but go ahead.

00:07:43.729 --> 00:07:45.698 line:95%,end
NIA: <i>Abby pushes us to work harder</i>

00:07:45.765 --> 00:07:48.167 line:5%,start
every single day that we see her.

00:07:48.234 --> 00:07:49.836 line:95%,end
Why are you so sloppy?

